title: Edencomer Apple Picker, 4.3M Long Telescopic Handle Fruit Picker with Fabric Bag Holder and Drawstring Storage Bag, 10 Sections Fruit Grabber for Picking Fruits
features: Efficient Fruit Picker - The length of this fruit picker can reach 4.2m, and the fruit picking rake is equipped with a deep and large metal basket with a cushion, which can hold multiple fruits at once. Our fruit picking tools include 10 extension rods, 2 adjustable clamps, 1 fruit picking basket and 1 elastic foam pad.

Easy Installation of Fruit Picker - The fruit picker has an upgraded metal clip that allows you to tighten the basket only by hand, without the need for a screwdriver. It is equipped with a foam pad to protect the fruit from bumps. Finally, the basket and the rod are connected together, and the whole installation can be completed by hand tightening.

Upgraded Basket Lock - the basket lock of the fruit picker adopts 2 detachable upgraded locks, which are more sturdy than the original. Place the fruit between the hooks and gently pull to complete the fruit picking process. Please ensure that all installations are securely fastened before use.

Durable - Our fruit picker is made of very durable materials, lightweight, and will not bend or wear out after repeated use. The rod is adjustable and the height can be adjusted according to the fruit you need to pick, making it perfect for the harvest season.
Fruit Picker can Pick a Variety of Fruits: the fruit picker with a basket is suitable for most fruit trees, such as apples, pears, oranges, mangoes, lemons, papayas, peaches, grapefruits, etc.
